Interface CmdObserver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    View
    public interface CmdObserver
    Part of a simplified observer design pattern. Represents objects which are observers of the command pane, which the command pane can signal whenever its state is updated.
    Author:
    Goh Khian Wei
